{"tid":2177869,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"海外專家斥：圖將示威者變暴徒","createTime":"2020-08-28T04:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T05:05:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b1feecb4a7f74bf7ed5f2cf3658e3ea0146f92a3","tid":2177869,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T04:31:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200828/V37CK56EV5BDLO4RFRVHOE2HEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200828%2FV37CK56EV5BDLO4RFRVHOE2HEM%2F&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONkYzBSotcsoJ75UENuGtOl4%3D&h=fbac74e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200828%2FV37CK56EV5BDLO4RFRVHOE2HEM%2F&h=2242dae5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200828/V37CK56EV5BDLO4RFRVHOE2HEM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n海外專家斥：圖將示威者變暴徒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PEcdTVF_xzczKyFwMKJlb5E1EAQ=/886x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BH7XYRDBA5C7ZBPFXVJXDMDJPQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPEcdTVF_xzczKyFwMKJlb5E1EAQ%3D%2F886x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBH7XYRDBA5C7ZBPFXVJXDMDJPQ.jpg&h=a802f36f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nClifford Stott<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方就去年7.21元朗事件拘捕民主黨立法會議員林卓廷，惹起公憤。前監警會國際專家小組成員、英國學者Clifford Stott昨亦在Twitter發文，斥責警方顯然是要改寫歷史，以符合警方將示威者變「非理性暴徒」的立場。「大家不應驚訝香港官方推翻2019年的香港歷史，以求將示威群眾描述成不理性的暴民」，認為警方處理7.21事件的手法，反映警方與特區政府聯合打擊香港民主運動。<br />\n<br />\nStott續指，警察經常形容「暴徒」背後是受外國勢力操控，甚或是收錢行事，但他從來沒有看過相關證據，並強調「沒有甚麼比事實更真實。」他亦提到，從政者經常以人群理論來否認示威者抗議的合法基礎，以掩蓋政府建立「群眾暴力」及警察以武力維持社會秩序的合法化。<br />\n<br />\n去年監警會委託五名外。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n曾調查7.21等多宗反送。。。。。。"},{"pid":"54685e53b1062b22e792b44f707509619f6ecaae","tid":2177869,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":